Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur4.5\pos(229.5,768)}鯨魚、翱翔藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在天上飛呢 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是鯨魚喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鯨魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 雖然我也沒親眼見過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}它一直在世界各地四處飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以是很難親眼一見的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是今年居然會路過這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 而且它現在還飛得相當低
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}趁這機會去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}一定要看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼時候會過來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}明天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}糟了 它已經到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒時間了 趕快準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}七分鐘後在門口集合 OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}收到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼了 現在還這麼早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我可以出門一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}可以啊 要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我去看鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鯨魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏就坐我的掃帚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好久沒飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不痛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}已經掌握技巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這裡就是預計會通過的地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}希望它還沒有經過呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們把這個塗在眼皮上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鯨魚平時會擬態成雲朵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不塗這個是看不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏 把瀏海撩起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴也塗一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒什麼味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.24,0:05:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}姐姐 是不是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就是藏在雲朵深處的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}小小的 長長的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哪個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.79,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}形狀就像鯨魚 肯定是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們靠近一點看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害 鯨魚在天上飛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}下一步 我們登上它的背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}可以登上去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不好意思 我們想乘上你的背
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}長滿了草
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好壯觀 這是遺蹟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 很久以前好像還有人住在這
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好寬敞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大概是座神殿之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}飛得好高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是我們之前採莢果蕨的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你看 就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鯨魚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還真是很久以前就存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.12,0:07:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.73,0:08:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}看來這裡就是頭頂尖了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有人在喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}先到一步的客人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.30,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45}An…An…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.30,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}杏…杏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你好
