Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(960,982.5)}Anzu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來是杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}茜姐 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}杏子也來看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 早就期待能親眼見見它了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}杏子很喜歡有歷史的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 興趣很古雅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}特等席
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.52,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}據說以前鯨魚們都是成群飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}自從在背上生活的人們消失後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}他們就各自遨遊世界去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有其他的鯨魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}現在已經確認還有其他三條
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但是說不定還不止這幾條
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.60,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}杏子對鯨魚可真了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}只是聽別人這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.31,0:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真厲害 將來要當考古學家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.07,0:09:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但願可以當上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那你有練習開礦車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有練習被大岩石追著到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}考古學家應該不做那些事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}畢竟還沒吃早餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說起來我也還沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那雖然有點不捨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們也該下去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.51,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}杏子 有空來我家吃頓飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對啊 來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我還想多聽點鯨魚的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就恭敬不如從命了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還有我珍藏的超好吃的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}孩子的爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喔 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.09,0:10:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}千夏去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好像去看鯨魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鯨魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:10:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對 鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}喔 真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}話說你在哪 不在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 鯨魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}什麼 你去海邊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯…啊 應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哦 你住在這裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 寄住在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好棒 小別墅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}古色古香很有情趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 我很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這裡好嗎 房子很舊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:12:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不 就是舊才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我可以留幾張照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}他是阿圭 還記得他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 很怕鬼怪的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}都被知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.58,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}奈奈阿姨 我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:34.32,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哥哥 早餐吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好久沒吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎 前陣子也吃過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}前陣子都已經是一個月前了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就是前陣子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}肯尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好久沒見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}過得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你們認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 經常和茜姐一起光顧我們店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 我們去看鯨魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}就跟肯尼你說的一樣 真壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我調查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}果然還是覺得你告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}居民消失一說最接近真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣啊 還有不少謎團呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來肯尼小姐也這麼了解鯨魚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真琴你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}肯尼的興趣是做人類學之類的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}包括那些鯨魚 她也獨自環遊世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}跑去看了幾十遍來做研究
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她還是我老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:54.72,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真了不起 還是前輩的老師呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.19,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我不是前輩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}貓在研究人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:58.55,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是另有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}又是一位可愛的小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是我打擾了 我叫椎名杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我是圭與千夏的母親 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不請自來非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不會啦 如果不介意我們家的粗茶淡飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不用客氣 盡管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 我也有東西想招待你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我想想 還需要點雞蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不知道夠不夠用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嚐嚐看吧 醃櫻桃蘿蔔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是真琴姐種的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}但蘿蔔跟鬆餅不太搭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}果然是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不過味道真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我家還有不少 你就盡管吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這份報紙好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我說的沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這是奇多小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你看這裡寫著歌唱的馬鈴薯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯啊 最近才發現的新品種
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}肚子會吃壞的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}噓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哥哥已經變身鬆餅機了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 我現在只會專心做鬆餅了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哥哥很會做鬆餅的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}能烤出厚厚的鬆餅 跟鬆餅機一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎 還要加一層麵糊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.89,0:16:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 加層甜甜圈狀麵糊就能烤出厚度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我想吃甜甜圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真的耶 一下子就膨脹開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}再蓋上蓋子烤一下就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}圭會成為好妻子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}居然是妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 杏子姐知道鬆餅的歷史嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}有好多種說法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.95,0:16:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}你還真知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}傳說鬆餅發源於古埃及
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}是混合砂糖 水與小麥粉烤出的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}大約70餘年前傳入日本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}聽說最早售賣的鬆餅粉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}為了便於做紅豆餅 所以沒有加砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以沒什麼人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}也沒激發出太大影響
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}後來加入砂糖的鬆餅粉走上貨架
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.91,0:17:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}才聚集起人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}當時飲食文化又盛行西洋風
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以鬆餅才借東風走進了百姓生活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}順帶一提 鬆餅這名字是日本的造詞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(810,982.5)}hot cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}國外幾乎都稱之為鬆餅的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fs45\pos(1192.5,982.5)}pan cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來鬆餅和鬆餅是同樣的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(690,982.5)\blur4.5}pan cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(900,982.5)\blur4.5}hot cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 在做法上幾乎完全一致
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}鬆餅的pan源於煎鍋一詞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\blur4.5\pos(667.5,982.5)}pan cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\blur4.5\pos(1110,982.5)}frypan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}含義就是「能用煎鍋輕鬆製作的糕餅」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以用煎鍋做出的鬆餅也是鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1095,982.5)\blur4.5}hot cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\blur4.5\pos(1357.5,982.5)}pan cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}硬要說有什麼不同的話 就是厚度了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}厚的是鬆餅 而薄的是鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(847.5,982.5)\blur4.5}hot cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1267.5,982.5)\blur4.5}pan cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這麼說來哥哥做的就是鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\pos(1297.5,982.5)\blur4.5}hot cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好厲害 杏子什麼都知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}談不上什麼都知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了 傳入日本是明治時期的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那就遠不止70餘年前了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}那是奇多和肯尼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯 來吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}杏子 你住哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沿著前面的路走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}穿過樹叢隧道就能到的一家咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒聽說過有咖啡店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我家藏得比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我下次能做客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}恭候光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}很厲害的 有幽靈服務生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}哦 就是前幾天說過的那家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}在眼前一下消失 又一下冒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別說啦別說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.01,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}老是談幽靈 幽靈真的會聚過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}不會的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}忘記跟家裡說一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對不起 我能借用一下電話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}請用 就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}真是個好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}媽媽 我是杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 看到了 真是壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}還正好碰上了真琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}對 就是前幾天那位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}她請我去她家吃東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}所以我會晚點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}這樣啊 我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}別忘了好好道謝喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯 我知道 那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}杏子你等一下 茜在你身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我能開一下窗戶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}開吧 想透個氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}最近天氣一下就暖和起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}貓頭鷹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}牠是杏子姐的使魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}原來是使魔呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}嚇我一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}抱歉 媽媽有東西想交給茜姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}給我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}好久不見了 奧羅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}我看看寫了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5}客人賒了不少帳 下次來結清吧
